{"tid":1257703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"626/627活動整合","createTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T03:03:32.000Z","uid":113373,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f9991a6f7d0e915f4ff17f8de75a7004e580aa2e","tid":1257703,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馬拉松式領事館請願<br />\n6&bull;26 星期三<br />\n9AM 中環遮打花園集合</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n舉辦方已經同警方協調好三條遊行路線。<br />\n由於已經約好領事館請願時間，<span style=\"color: red;\">請各位準時上午九時到遮打花園會合</span>。請穿著輕便黑色衣物，可配戴口罩。帶備足夠食水及乾糧，並攜帶雨具。遊行隊伍將一同靜默遊行往美國，歐盟及英國領事館，然後分成三隊前往其他領事館。參加者可以預先考慮選擇的路線，屆時按照指示分批前行。預計所有路線會在下午四時前結束。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如要參加明天領事館請願活動，請加入telegram：<br />\n<br />\n交流谷<br />\n@g20helphk<br />\n<br />\n行程頻道<br />\n@seekforg20help<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44B5DSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44B5DSV.png&h=973b1ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g19yNMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg19yNMi.png&h=7739a5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5vuk6m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5vuk6m.png&h=90836699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民陣 G20 Free Hong Kong 集會<br />\n6&bull;26 星期三<br />\n8PM 中環愛丁堡廣場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49nAgGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49nAgGi.jpg&h=f7e12bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民自發行動<br />\n6&bull;27 星期四<br />\n10AM 中環律政中心</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k21JqAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk21JqAM.jpg&h=28ef4da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niDLDVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniDLDVN.png&h=a33afe87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52dc8ea247f9447bbce03a0a8b00f902a9fcca32","tid":1257703,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac55f8a15207845aae802907d154534f9c9f572","tid":1257703,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJn1ce0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJn1ce0.png&h=0aeb1555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/seekforg20help\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fseekforg20help&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ad2ace46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/seekforg20help</a><br />\n由於聽日步行路線比較複雜，所以我地會用呢個頻道keep住update遊行隊伍去到咩位置，方便想中途加入既人搵到我地。所以希望大家可以幫手share呢條Channel出去，感謝！<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></div><br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738938ebdc785aad77b32a54a8322fcfbd05aa7e","tid":1257703,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1b1b257582454e98a0dc009974a04138cffea0","tid":1257703,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"630642909a82c61489bc08630299fc581fed2fb6","tid":125770